{"tid":660172,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲唔要ps4可以讓比我","createTime":"2018-05-10T13:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T11:17:03.000Z","uid":181819,"like":35,"dislike":1670,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"7841faaa386ca2b82529ef1991fef3f1abe981bb","tid":660172,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買PS4<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想去讀電競 買部PS4 幾百蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾百蚊食到一個星期了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手PS4 讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有部打到FIFA既PS4 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e203a50369b701be62e9033c3e7a298af8342470","tid":660172,"uid":163554,"like":663,"dislike":5,"score":658,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d13b134b56b29c45f44fc6ac9531a57934495a5","tid":660172,"uid":531,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"男定女？男嘅去搵份pt自己搵錢"},{"pid":"e871a45734e8dcc64e77e275fc3100ff37009861","tid":660172,"uid":33819,"like":252,"dislike":0,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"太長 零分重作"},{"pid":"94dc0bc6fa96ac87bc7d87d5c3366779e6e46168","tid":660172,"uid":44210,"like":40,"dislike":152,"score":-112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"女既比我屌10獲比你<br />\n仔既你屌我10獲"},{"p